# Styling Conventions

Rules for styling components with Tailwind CSS and shadcn CSS variables.

## CSS Variables (Tokens)

### shadcn CSS Variable System

We use shadcn/ui's CSS variable system. All CSS variables are defined in `src/styles/globals.css`.

```css
:root {
  --background: 0 0% 100%;
  --foreground: 222.2 84% 4.9%;
  
  --primary: 222.2 47.4% 11.2%;
  --primary-foreground: 210 40% 98%;
  
  --secondary: 210 40% 96.1%;
  --secondary-foreground: 222.2 47.4% 11.2%;
  
  --muted: 210 40% 96.1%;
  --muted-foreground: 215.4 16.3% 46.9%;
  
  --accent: 210 40% 96.1%;
  --accent-foreground: 222.2 47.4% 11.2%;
  
  --destructive: 0 84.2% 60.2%;
  --destructive-foreground: 210 40% 98%;
  
  --border: 214.3 31.8% 91.4%;
  --input: 214.3 31.8% 91.4%;
  --ring: 222.2 84% 4.9%;
  
  --radius: 0.5rem;
}
```

### Available CSS Variables

| Variable | Purpose | Usage Example |
|----------|---------|---------------|
| `--background` | Page/card backgrounds | `bg-background` |
| `--foreground` | Primary text | `text-foreground` |
| `--primary` | Primary actions | `bg-primary` |
| `--primary-foreground` | Text on primary | `text-primary-foreground` |
| `--secondary` | Secondary actions | `bg-secondary` |
| `--secondary-foreground` | Text on secondary | `text-secondary-foreground` |
| `--muted` | Subtle backgrounds | `bg-muted` |
| `--muted-foreground` | Supporting text | `text-muted-foreground` |
| `--accent` | Hover/focus states | `bg-accent` |
| `--accent-foreground` | Text on accent | `text-accent-foreground` |
| `--destructive` | Destructive actions | `bg-destructive` |
| `--destructive-foreground` | Text on destructive | `text-destructive-foreground` |
| `--border` | Component borders | `border-border` |
| `--input` | Input borders | `border-input` |
| `--ring` | Focus rings | `ring-ring` |
| `--radius` | Border radius | `rounded-[--radius]` |

## Never Hardcode Values

### Colors

```tsx
// ❌ WRONG - Hardcoded colors
className="bg-blue-600 text-white"
className="bg-gray-100 text-gray-900"
className="border-slate-300"

// ✅ CORRECT - CSS variables
className="bg-primary text-primary-foreground"
className="bg-muted text-foreground"
className="border-border"
```

### Spacing

```tsx
// ❌ WRONG - Arbitrary values without reason
className="px-[23px] py-[17px]"
className="gap-[15px]"

// ✅ CORRECT - Tailwind scale
className="px-4 py-2"      // 16px, 8px
className="gap-4"          // 16px
className="space-y-6"      // 24px
```

### Border Radius

```tsx
// ❌ WRONG - Hardcoded radius
className="rounded-md"
className="rounded-lg"

// ✅ CORRECT - Radius token
className="rounded-[--radius]"
```

